### Test Goal Template Usage Stats and Goal Creation
### Step 1: Get all templates to find a template ID
GET http://localhost:3000/goal-templates
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###
### Step 2: Get the current usage count for a specific template (replace with actual template ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/goal-templates/TEMPLATE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###
### Step 3: Create a goal from the template (this should increment usage count)
POST http://localhost:3000/goal-templates/TEMPLATE_ID_HERE/use
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Goal from Template",
  "description": "Testing template usage tracking",
  "dueDate": "2025-09-25"
}

###
### Step 4: Check the template again to verify usage count increased
GET http://localhost:3000/goal-templates/TEMPLATE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###
### Step 5: Check the goals list to verify the goal was created with templateId
GET http://localhost:3000/goals
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###
### Step 6: Get usage stats for the template (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:3000/goal-templates/TEMPLATE_ID_HERE/usage-stats
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###
### Step 7: Get overall template analytics (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:3000/goal-templates/analytics
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###
### Step 8: Get category statistics (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:3000/goal-templates/category-stats
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###
### Step 9: Check admin dashboard (this should not error with date issues)
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
